  "rationale": "Single hero reusing the seeded project pattern hero-display-over-staggered-media verbatim in structure: centered stack on surface/inverse, two hard-edged photos with the smaller portrait offset right crossing the landscape's lower edge (media-over-media overlap + stagger), sanctioned display-title-over-media, gold accent reserved for the display title only, measured spacing, asset:null for measured brand photography. The ONE varied axis is scale contrast: the headline collapses to the single monumental word 'WOODWAVE' (colossal display tier) while the measured subhead is distilled to a terse caption-length lede, dropping a tier so the display line dominates. Eyebrow and CTA remain verbatim. novelty adapt, seededFrom the seeded hero pattern."
